{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n156\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 1\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 81 + 45 + 6 = 132\u2081\u2080\n\n711\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 567 + 9 + 1 = 577\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n132 \u00d7 577 = 132 \u00d7 (500 + 77)\n= 132 \u00d7 500 + 132 \u00d7 77\n= 66,000 + 10,164\n= 76,164\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n76164 \u00f7 9 = 8462 r 6\n8462 \u00f7 9 = 940 r 2\n940 \u00f7 9 = 104 r 4\n104 \u00f7 9 = 11 r 5\n11 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 2\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: 125426\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n125426\u2089 = 1\u00d759049 + 2\u00d76561 + 5\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 6\u00d71\n= 59049 + 13122 + 3645 + 324 + 18 + 6\n= 76,164\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n125426", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 468}